    Class Description
    ErrorController
    Spring controller for runtime errors.

    A Spring Boot parking Internet of Things (IoT) application.

    ParkingLotController
    Spring Boot controller class for ParkingLot class.
    ParkingLotHelper
    Helper class designed to create example parking lots, consisting of rows, and their spaces.

    Transaction involving a parking space.
